WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Welcome to RestoreAssist.

00:02.000 --> 00:05.619
This guide shows you how to sign in to your account.

00:05.619 --> 00:11.675
Navigate to restoreassist dot app and click the Sign In button in the top right corner.

00:11.675 --> 00:17.731
Enter your email address and password, or use Google single sign-on for instant access.

00:17.731 --> 00:23.995
If you have two-factor authentication enabled, enter the code from your authenticator app.

00:23.995 --> 00:30.000
You are now signed in to your dashboard, ready to manage inspections and generate reports.